script-data-source.name: Elastic search

oda-data-set.name: force_flat_layout
oda-data-set.xml-property: SELECT `inspector_name`, count(`customer_name`) as customer_count FROM `force_flat_layout` GROUP BY `inspector_name`

oda-data-set.name: flat_layout
oda-data-set.xml-property: SELECT t1.data as inspector, count(t2.data) as customer FROM `flat_layout` as t1 join flat_layout as t2 on t1.submission_id = t2.submission_id and t1.entry_label='Inspector Name' and t2.entry_label = 'Customer Name' group by inspector
